{"category": "interview-question", "node": {"id": "5433592", "title": "Uber | Phone Screen | Sub Counting", "commentCount": 16, "viewCount": 891, "post": {"id": 7936282, "creationDate": 1720338400, "voteCount": 6, "author": null}}, "topic": {"id": 5433592, "title": "Uber | Phone Screen | Sub Counting", "viewCount": 891, "post": {"id": 7936282, "creationDate": 1720338400, "voteCount": 6, "content": "Given an array A of length n and a 2D array B which consists of m queries.\\nEach query is one of the following two types:\\n\\n\\u2022 Type 1- L R 0: Find the number of non-decreasing subarrays in the range from L to R.\\n\\u2022 Type 2 - L R X: Replace every element in the range from L to R with X where X != 0.\\nFind the sum of answers to queries of Type 1", "author": null}}, "comments": [{"id": 2516426, "post": {"id": 7996030, "content": "location ?\\n", "voteCount": 2, "creationDate": 1720969524, "author": {"username": "malhotrashubham2802"}}}, {"id": 2724773, "post": {"id": 8779004, "content": "Which role?", "voteCount": 1, "creationDate": 1731754292, "author": {"username": "hnagubady"}}}, {"id": 2567858, "post": {"id": 8189638, "content": "will O(n*m) solution work?", "voteCount": 1, "creationDate": 1723316237, "author": {"username": "Admiral_puri"}}}, {"id": 2557590, "post": {"id": 8147773, "content": "Segment Tree + DP", "voteCount": 1, "creationDate": 1722790706, "author": {"username": "rnotappl"}}}, {"id": 2521171, "post": {"id": 8013021, "content": "Op can u elaborate a bit more? seems to be DSU, not entirely sure. \\nbut as far as the description says : u r modifying the board and the calculatig the answer of the query at each step ", "voteCount": 1, "creationDate": 1721187962, "author": {"username": "malhotrashubham2802"}}}, {"id": 2520743, "post": {"id": 8011525, "content": "location?", "voteCount": 1, "creationDate": 1721156619, "author": {"username": "DeepshikhaZ"}}}, {"id": 2499505, "post": {"id": 7936999, "content": "This can be done by segment tree along with suffix and prefix calculation to maintain sorted order", "voteCount": 1, "creationDate": 1720344085, "author": {"username": "sahil_77"}}}]}